description:
100% safe = 0% free.
ANYTIME THE GOVERNMENT SAYS ""It's for your safety"", you know they are taking your rights away and stealing your liberty to make your own decisions regarding your health or safety. 
Freedom is never granted, we were born with unalienable rights, they are called birth rights. I am all for people voluntarily locking down and wearing a mask if thats what they want..... I draw the line when authorities or people  mandate that we all must do the same.
